    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a budget-friendly project car? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has seen better days and shows significant wear, both inside and out. There are notable mechanical and cosmetic issues that will need attention, so it's best suited for a handy buyer or someone looking for a parts vehicle. That said, it's priced accordingly, making it a great opportunity for the right person willing to put in some work!",
      "price": 5500.0,
